author: alexdma
msg: - Refactorer,  Refactor Engine and ReasoningServiceExecutor now handle OWLAPI/Clerezza conversions as TripleCollection objects (STANBOL-337)
- New ontology input source that supports Clerezza graphs (STANBOL-332)
- Clerezza ontology storage now converts straight to Clerezza Tc's without passing through Jena converters (STANBOL-332)
- RootOntologyIRISource now has a parameter for ignoring the offlinemode (which was not really supported by the earlier version) (STANBOL-178)
- ONManager API can now provide its offline configuration (STANBOL-178)
- Stricter unit test assertions for OntoNet offline mode (STANBOL-178)
- Removed even more deprecated Registry API methods (STANBOL-285)
- Refactorer POM now specifies Xerces version to avoid conflicts (STANBOL-301)
- Fixed typo in DuplicateIDEception method name
